    "brief_html": "<p>Response for both <a href=\"/packet/102/sid-optionalwork\">S&gt;C 0x4A SID_OPTIONALWORK</a> and <a href=\"/packet/182/sid-requiredwork\">S&gt;C 0x4C SID_REQUIREDWORK</a>. See <a href=\"/document/43/extrawork\">ExtraWork</a> document for more details.</p>",
